messages.message: Thank you for connecting!
Hey, forgot to tell you I'VE STRUCK GOLD! with those scripts from Bryan. Fantastic! :P
Uhhhh, what the heck happened to you Brian? Is everything good?

Yeah. I just felt a bit isolated, I think it was making me crazy. Sorry if anything I said yesterday worried you, I didn't mean for anything dramatic to change by today or tomorrow. I was just thinking ahead. I am glad you asked ;)
I'd like to have double date lunch sometime.
Also I've never heard the phrase "pie in the sky" used in a work setting before. Lol

Michael Hayashi asked where you were and I replied that you were likely busy developing changes for startups and we'll probably see you in Wired within 5 years. So I'm going to need you to prove me right, k
Lunch or drinks with our significant others sounds great.
Don't stress though. You're destined for greatness
Thank you. I'll keep learning.
